    <node id="Atherogenic Dyslipidemia">
      <data key="d0">Atherogenic Dyslipidemia</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Atherogenic dyslipidemia is characterized by elevated triglyceride, small LDL particles, and low HDL cholesterol, defining the Metabolic Syndrome.</data>
